#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_leasing
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_rental
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well. We are pleased to confirm the leasing arrangement for the\n"
"                    following asset:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    Lease Start Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('start_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Lease End Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    As per the agreement, please ensure timely payment of the lease fees and adhere to the terms\n"
"                    outlined therein.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Should you have any questions or require further clarification regarding the lease\n"
"                    agreement, feel free to contact us at your convenience.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<IV>\n"
"Dragi\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('kupac') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Nadam se da će vas ova e -pošta dobro pronaći.Zadovoljstvo nam je potvrditi aranžman za zakup za\n"
"Sljedeća imovina:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ime imovine:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('imovina') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"Datum početka zakupa:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('start_date') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Datum kraja zakupa:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Prema sporazumu, molimo osigurajte pravovremeno plaćanje naknada za zakup i pridržavajte se uvjeta\n"
"opisano u njemu.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako imate bilo kakvih pitanja ili zahtijevate daljnje pojašnjenje u vezi s najma\n"
"Sporazum, slobodno nas kontaktirajte na vašu udobnost.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako imate bilo kakvih pitanja ili trebate daljnju pomoć, ne ustručavajte se kontaktirati nas.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Najbolje pozdrav,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</IV>\n"
"</IV>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_leased_assent_return_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is a friendly reminder regarding the return of the leased asset,\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>\n"
"                    , which is due\n"
"                    for return as per our lease agreement on\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>\n"
"                    .\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure that the asset is returned on or before the specified return date to avoid any\n"
"                    potential late fees or penalties as outlined in our agreement.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<IV>\n"
"Dragi\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('kupac') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ovo je prijateljski podsjetnik u vezi s povratkom iznajmljene imovine,\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('imovina') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b>\n"
", što je posljedica\n"
"za povrat prema našem ugovoru o zakupu\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b>\n"
".\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Molimo osigurajte da se imovina vraća na ili prije navedenog datuma povratka kako biste izbjegli bilo koji\n"
"Potencijalne kasne naknade ili kazne kako je navedeno u našem sporazumu.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako imate bilo kakvih pitanja ili trebate daljnju pomoć, ne ustručavajte se kontaktirati nas.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Najbolje pozdrav,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</IV>\n"
"</IV>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_assent_rental_invoice_due_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is a friendly reminder regarding the upcoming payment for the rental asset invoice.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    As per our agreement, the payment for the asset\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>is due on\n"
"                    <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('due_date') or not_available\">,</t></b>\n"
"                    . However, it appears that\n"
"                    the payment has not yet been received.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure that the payment is made promptly to avoid any late fees or disruptions to your rental\n"
"                    agreement. Your cooperation in this matter is greatly appreciated.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder, and kindly inform us of the\n"
"                    transaction details for our records.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<IV>\n"
"Dragi\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('kupac') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ovo je prijateljski podsjetnik u vezi s nadolazećem plaćanjem za fakturu imovine za najam.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Prema našem sporazumu, plaćanje imovine\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('imovina') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b> dospijeva na\n"
"<b> <t t-out = \"ctx.get ('dupe_date') ili not_available\">, </t> </b>\n"
".Međutim, čini se da\n"
"Plaćanje još nije primljeno.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Molimo osigurajte da se plaćanje izvrši kako bi se izbjegle kasne naknade ili poremećaje vašeg najamnina\n"
"sporazum.Vaša je suradnja u ovom pitanju jako cijenjena.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako ste već izvršili uplatu, zanemarite ovaj podsjetnik i ljubazno nas obavijestite o\n"
"Pojedinosti o transakciji za naše evidencije.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako imate bilo kakvih pitanja ili trebate daljnju pomoć, ne ustručavajte se kontaktirati nas.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Najbolje pozdrav,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</IV>\n"
"</IV>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_assignment
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('employee') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I am pleased to inform you that the following asset have been assigned to you:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Assign Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('assign_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please take good care of the assigned asset and ensure they are used responsibly in accordance\n"
"                    with our organization's policies and guidelines.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Should you encounter any issues or have any\n"
"                    questions regarding the assigned asset, please feel free to reach out to us for assistance.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<IV>\n"
"<IV>\n"
"Dragi\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('zaposlenik') ili not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Nadam se da će vas ova e -pošta dobro pronaći.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Drago mi je što vas mogu obavijestiti da vam je dodijeljena sljedeća imovina:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ime imovine:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('imovina') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Datum dodjele:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('dodjeljak_date') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Molimo vas da se dobro pobrinete za dodijeljenu imovinu i osigurajte da se odgovorno koriste u skladu\n"
"s politikama i smjernicama naše organizacije.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako naiđete na bilo koje probleme ili imate bilo koje\n"
"Pitanja koja se tiču ​​dodijeljene imovine, slobodno nam se obratite za pomoć.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako imate bilo kakvih pitanja ili trebate daljnju pomoć, ne ustručavajte se kontaktirati nas.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Najbolje pozdrav,\n"
"<br>\n"
"\n"
"</IV>\n"
"</IV>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_reservation
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('employee') or not_available\">,</t>,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is to confirm that your reservation for the following asset has been successfully processed:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Reservation start Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('start_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Reservation End Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure to adhere to the reservation schedule.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<IV>\n"
"<IV>\n"
"Dragi\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('zaposlenik') ili not_available\">, </t>,\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Nadam se da će vas ova e -pošta dobro pronaći.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ovo je potvrditi da je vaša rezervacija za sljedeću imovinu uspješno obrađena:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ime imovine:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('imovina') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Datum početka rezervacije:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('start_date') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Datum kraja rezervacije:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') ili not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Molimo osigurajte da se pridržavate rasporeda rezervacije.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ako imate bilo kakvih pitanja ili trebate daljnju pomoć, ne ustručavajte se kontaktirati nas.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Najbolje pozdrav,\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"</IV>\n"
"</IV>"

